{"tid":1669893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肥人最撚鍾意打飛機！健身啦香港人！","createTime":"2019-10-22T22:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T14:30:13.000Z","uid":72143,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a777117765ba26c1e03e2cb43bbe2228470e36e","tid":1669893,"uid":72143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:42:06.000Z","msg":"減肥啦懵撚 多多籍口！<br />\n仲成撚日講小肚腩代表有錢代表媾到女<br />\n根本得啲濕尻中產先會肥 做奴隸做到冇哂時間做運動 再唔係懶閪 hea撚到碌木咁<br />\n你睇下全球十大富豪 有幾多個肥人？ <br />\n個撚個用腦用到瘦哂啦 就算香港首富都係瘦到乜咁 點解呀 因為人地個腦大過你個死人肚呀 肥撚懵你真係 管理好自己身體先真男人 <br />\n<br />\n再講 家下咩時勢 周街黑社會 唔操fit啲點跑得快過啲狗 上次大圍個藍衫小肚腩 差佬一下推跌咗佢 好撚柒 <br />\n點忍呀？ 男人老狗俾人推跌 起返身又知唔夠抽<br />\n721個瘦仔直頭跪地 俾人打 <br />\n香港人就快連尊嚴都冇呀 仲講媾女 <br />\n<br />\n操呀 香港人 自己都保護唔到 點保護女人 下一代 仲呢個家園呀<br />\n你係黑社會嘅 你都揀啲好恰嘅嚟打啦 <br />\n一句講哂 武力源於保護 <br />\n香港人健身呀！"},{"pid":"a23f4a937f948dda3dcd2d13dc0d9ce5f00b16e3","tid":1669893,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:53:42.000Z","msg":"閲"},{"pid":"54261f8484fb43156ec67fe7df318cdc42f7c4eb","tid":1669893,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n56eS0r.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn56eS0r.gif&h=298c73ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f72f11f5fa53543a4f7355f351326ecd105f6b73","tid":1669893,"uid":72143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a23f4a937f948dda3dcd2d13dc0d9ce5f00b16e3","tid":1669893,"uid":303977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:53:42.000Z","msg":"閲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"減肥啦"},{"pid":"3ee3ca0a76814b10e087c60328122aaefb3ad0fc","tid":1669893,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T23:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0tT8DD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0tT8DD.jpg&h=d03978d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5262005a2d171d4a8a468f9